title: Russian fighter jets enter Syria with transponders off
text:
25 Russian fighter jets enter Syria with transponders off 
CNN: A U.S. official told CNN Thursday that Russian fighter jets turned off their transponders as they flew into Syria in an apparent attempt to avoid detection. The official said the fighters flew very close to a transport plane that had its transponder on and functioning.U.S. satellites rapidly saw that the aircraft were there, according to the official.
